   <conbody>
      <div class="- topic/div ">
         <p class="- topic/p ">By default, 3 relays are available on the controller. If more
relays are needed additional cards can be used.</p>
         <p class="- topic/p ">Each input/output
card have 4 potential-free change-over (CO) relays. Multiple cards
can be used if needed.</p>
         <note class="- topic/note ">If multiple input/output cards are
used, each card must have a unique address. The address is set using
jumpers.</note>
